<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 22:07:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列在加沙南部发布更多撤离令，缩小“安全区”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-more-evacuation-orders-in-south-gaza-shrinking-safe-zone/00000191-61fe-dd29-a7f3-65ff11b10000</link><description>联合国表示，大多数加沙人已经流离失所，其中许多人被迫多次撤离，而且在整个战争期间，约 84% 的加沙地区已被疏散</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 21:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-more-evacuation-orders-in-south-gaza-shrinking-safe-zone/00000191-61fe-dd29-a7f3-65ff11b10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队命名两名在加沙战斗中丧生的预备役军人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-two-reservists-killed-in-gaza-fighting/00000191-61fa-d1d3-a5f7-71fe32c20000</link><description>约塔姆·伊扎克·佩莱德（Yotam Itzhak Peled）军官（后任）和莫迪凯·约瑟夫·本·肖姆（Mordechai Yosef Ben Shoam）少校（后任）均 34 岁，在加沙中部被爆炸装置炸死</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 21:26:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-names-two-reservists-killed-in-gaza-fighting/00000191-61fa-d1d3-a5f7-71fe32c20000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔让伊朗了解情况，以色列距离释放人质协议又近了一步</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-team-cautiously-optimistic-after-hostage-release-talks-in-doha-netanyahu-says/00000191-61d8-d1d3-a5f7-71fe0eb50000</link><description>以色列消息人士澄清说，尽管多哈峰会在推进部分计划方面取得了“重大进展”，但仍在等待哈马斯的回应。正在努力安排周三在开罗举行的另一轮会谈</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 20:20:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-team-cautiously-optimistic-after-hostage-release-talks-in-doha-netanyahu-says/00000191-61d8-d1d3-a5f7-71fe0eb50000</guid></item><item><title>在谈判中持谨慎乐观态度的情况下，全国各地的以色列人呼吁达成释放人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/amid-cautious-optimism-in-talks-israelis-across-the-country-call-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-60d0-d017-abd9-f9f484c70000</link><description>“你得到了以色列人民的全力支持。人质的兄弟说：“不要羞于做出最道德、最犹太化的决定，把他们带回家。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 17:41:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/amid-cautious-optimism-in-talks-israelis-across-the-country-call-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-60d0-d017-abd9-f9f484c70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 316 天：加沙卫生官员称以色列国防军袭击导致加沙地带中部 17 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-316-gaza-health-officials-say-idf-strike-kills-17-in-central-strip/00000191-6146-d478-a99b-f77759c00000</link><description>巴勒斯坦人报告以色列对加沙中部的袭击造成 17 人死亡、数十人受伤 ■ 黎巴嫩卫生部：以色列袭击造成 10 人死亡；以色列国防军：袭击真主党武器储存设施 ■ 拜登官员：停火/人质协议谈判“现已进入最后阶段”。 ■ 以色列调查发现，以色列国防军士兵在周四的约旦河西岸定居者袭击中袖手旁观 ■ 以下是战争开始 316 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 17:14:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-316-gaza-health-officials-say-idf-strike-kills-17-in-central-strip/00000191-6146-d478-a99b-f77759c00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击造成十人死亡；真主党火箭弹袭击导致两名以色列国防军士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/ten-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-lebanon-hezbollah-rocket-barrage-wounds-two-idf-soldiers/00000191-6087-d1d3-a5f7-70ff66080000</link><description>以色列军队报告称，它袭击了黎巴嫩南部的真主党武器储存设施以及其他与恐怖活动有关的地点。当地卫生部门表示，受害者包括一名母亲和她的两个孩子</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/ten-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-lebanon-hezbollah-rocket-barrage-wounds-two-idf-soldiers/00000191-6087-d1d3-a5f7-70ff66080000</guid></item><item><title>卫生官员称，以色列对加沙中部的袭击造成至少17名巴勒斯坦人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-17/ty-article/at-least-17-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-central-gaza-health-officials-say/00000191-60af-dd29-a7f3-65efeb620000</link><description>据加沙卫生官员称，死者中有八名儿童和四名妇女。以色列军方表示正在调查有关此次袭击的报道</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 15:02:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-17/ty-article/at-least-17-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-central-gaza-health-officials-say/00000191-60af-dd29-a7f3-65efeb620000</guid></item><item><title>“脊髓灰质炎的最终疫苗是和平”：加沙首例脊髓灰质炎病例促使人们呼吁开展疫苗接种计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-17/ty-article/gazas-first-polio-case-prompts-calls-for-vaccination-program-cease-fire/00000191-609c-d1d3-a5f7-70fe39010000</link><description>联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯在代尔巴拉赫出现确诊病例后表示，以色列和哈马斯之间的战斗暂停对于为加沙人接种疫苗以预防这种高传染性疾病至关重要</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 14:46:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-08-17/ty-article/gazas-first-polio-case-prompts-calls-for-vaccination-program-cease-fire/00000191-609c-d1d3-a5f7-70fe39010000</guid></item><item><title>塔梅尔在纳布卢斯志愿担任护理人员。他在执行任务时被以色列导弹炸死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/tamer-was-a-volunteer-paramedic-he-was-killed-in-the-line-of-duty-by-an-israeli-missile/00000191-5e7a-d017-abd9-fffe803d0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦难民营的一名 21 岁志愿护理人员被以色列导弹炸死，尽管他身穿表明自己是医务人员的橙色背心。他在他姐姐计划举行婚礼的那天去世了。自加沙战争爆发以来，以色列国防军也加大了对约旦河西岸的空袭力度</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 04:24:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/tamer-was-a-volunteer-paramedic-he-was-killed-in-the-line-of-duty-by-an-israeli-missile/00000191-5e7a-d017-abd9-fffe803d0000</guid></item><item><title>即使政府腐败，这个组织也能拯救以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/even-when-the-government-is-corrupt-this-group-can-save-israel/00000191-5e5d-db59-a5d1-7f5dc75b0000</link><description>2011年，摩萨德首脑阻止了轰炸伊朗的决定，但到了2024年，国防领域已经没有人像梅厄·达甘那样能够阻止内塔尼亚胡了。有骨气的专业人士可以使以色列免遭全面战争、民主制度的破坏以及香蕉共和国的转型</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 03:55:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/even-when-the-government-is-corrupt-this-group-can-save-israel/00000191-5e5d-db59-a5d1-7f5dc75b0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们永远无法在极端分子的主场击败他们。中间派必须做完全相反的事情”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/well-never-defeat-extremists-in-their-home-court-centrists-must-do-the-exact-opposite/00000191-5e29-dd29-a7f3-7f696e770000</link><description>超过 30 名政治家、知识分子、学者和作家共同撰写了一本由 Yair Lapid 的高级政策顾问编辑的新书，解释了为什么中间主义是治疗极端主义的良药</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 03:23:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/well-never-defeat-extremists-in-their-home-court-centrists-must-do-the-exact-opposite/00000191-5e29-dd29-a7f3-7f696e770000</guid></item><item><title>两名哈马斯成员在以色列国防军对约旦河西岸的空袭中丧生；以色列袭击黎巴嫩目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-live/.premium/lebanese-reports-6-killed-3-wounded-in-israeli-attributed-strike-in-southern-lebanon/00000191-5e13-d180-a9fd-dffb39660000</link><description>巴勒斯坦报道：以色列对加沙中部难民营的袭击造成 17 人死亡 ■ 以色列空袭约旦河西岸杰宁的汽车，两名哈马斯成员丧生 ■ 卫生官员称，以色列对黎巴嫩南部的袭击造成 10 人死亡 ■ 以色列谈判小组对局势表示“谨慎乐观”内塔尼亚胡办公室称加沙人质协议 ■ 哈马斯高级官员：“最新一轮会谈没有就重大问题达成一致”</description><pubDate>Sat, 17 Aug 2024 02:22:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article-live/.premium/lebanese-reports-6-killed-3-wounded-in-israeli-attributed-strike-in-southern-lebanon/00000191-5e13-d180-a9fd-dffb39660000</guid></item><item><title>调查显示定居者袭击巴勒斯坦村庄时以色列国防军部队袖手旁观</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/investigation-shows-settler-raid-on-palestinian-village-took-place-in-front-of-idf-forces/00000191-5ce6-d7bf-a5b9-fcf66a940000</link><description>一名高级国防官员说，士兵们“没有采取任何行动来阻止大屠杀，他们只是站在旁边，看到了一切，却什么也没做。”被杀巴勒斯坦人的尸体已被带去尸检，但结果无法确定是谁射杀了他</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 22:18:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-17/ty-article/.premium/investigation-shows-settler-raid-on-palestinian-village-took-place-in-front-of-idf-forces/00000191-5ce6-d7bf-a5b9-fcf66a940000</guid></item><item><title>尽管发生了战争，议会平民准备委员会已经几个月没有召开会议了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/despite-war-knesset-committee-on-civilian-preparedness-hasnt-convened-for-months/00000191-5b80-d101-a7fd-7bbf13a30000</link><description>消息人士称，由于委员会讨论的议题较多，除了小组委员会的密切监督和深入讨论外，别无选择，距离小组委员会上次召开会议已经过去了四个月，这危及了以色列的国家安全</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 18:33:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/despite-war-knesset-committee-on-civilian-preparedness-hasnt-convened-for-months/00000191-5b80-d101-a7fd-7bbf13a30000</guid></item><item><title>“像我这样的犹太人不再在左派中感到受欢迎”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jews-like-me-no-longer-feel-welcome-on-the-left/00000191-50e4-d50b-adff-72e792a50000</link><description>对于澳大利亚最著名的记者之一、前自称为“反犹太复国主义联邦主义者”的迈克尔·加文达来说，10 月 7 日是一个警钟。随着他的祖国反犹太主义的高涨，特别是在他曾经视为盟友的群体中，他担心澳大利亚的犹太人</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 17:17:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2024-08-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jews-like-me-no-longer-feel-welcome-on-the-left/00000191-50e4-d50b-adff-72e792a50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列自以为强大，但从未如此依赖美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-thinks-its-strong-but-has-never-been-so-dependent-on-the-u-s/00000191-5b22-d392-a995-7fe6d4e10000</link><description>自10月7日以来，美国除了提供大规模军事援助外，还三度向中东派遣主力部队，帮助以色列对抗伊朗及其代理人。这是关系的悖论：在内塔尼亚胡的领导下，以色列感觉越强大，就越依赖美国</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 17:08:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-thinks-its-strong-but-has-never-been-so-dependent-on-the-u-s/00000191-5b22-d392-a995-7fe6d4e10000</guid></item><item><title>调解人称，美国提出停火建议，在以色列和哈马斯之间架起桥梁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-presents-cease-fire-proposal-that-bridges-israel-hamas-mediators-say/00000191-5bb4-d101-a7fd-7bbfda890000</link><description>据调解员称，该提案“有助于迅速实施协议” ■ 预计谈判将于下周在开罗继续进行</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 16:34:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-presents-cease-fire-proposal-that-bridges-israel-hamas-mediators-say/00000191-5bb4-d101-a7fd-7bbfda890000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 315 天：拜登称谈判各方“比以往任何时候都更接近”停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-315-biden-says-negotiating-parties-closer-than-ever-to-cease-fire/00000191-5bff-dc4c-a59f-7bff300f0001</link><description>停火/人质释放协议的谈判周五在卡塔尔继续进行，一位消息人士称，他们“到目前为止已经取得了成功” ■ 接近真主党的消息人士告诉《华盛顿邮报》，只要谈判正在进行，真主党就不会报复以色列多哈 ■ 以色列外长告诉英国和法国外长，“如果伊朗发动袭击，我们预计联军不仅会与以色列一起防御” ■ 战争已过去 315 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 16:26:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-315-biden-says-negotiating-parties-closer-than-ever-to-cease-fire/00000191-5bff-dc4c-a59f-7bff300f0001</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯人质的父亲说：“如果内塔尼亚胡想要达成协议，这次采访就不会进行”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/if-netanyahu-wanted-a-deal-this-interview-wouldnt-have-taken-place/00000191-5b72-d101-a7fd-7bffd9ed0000</link><description>伊齐克·霍恩（Itzik Horn）花了数周时间并承受巨大压力才得知他的两个儿子亚伊尔（Yair）和埃坦（Eitan）被关押在加沙。这位阿根廷出生的父亲猛烈抨击那些“背着人质”为加沙带来秩序的人，并建议内塔尼亚胡派他的儿子亚伊尔前往加沙，带回霍恩的儿子亚伊尔</description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 14:59:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-16/ty-article/.premium/if-netanyahu-wanted-a-deal-this-interview-wouldnt-have-taken-place/00000191-5b72-d101-a7fd-7bffd9ed0000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日已经足够令人震惊了。以色列人为何要粉饰这场悲剧？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/october-7-was-shocking-enough-why-should-israelis-embellish-the-tragedy/00000191-5a8b-d316-a9f1-decb1be60000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 16 Aug 2024 14:27:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/october-7-was-shocking-enough-why-should-israelis-embellish-the-tragedy/00000191-5a8b-d316-a9f1-decb1be60000</guid></item></channel></rss>